HW - BE A MAN CHALLENGE 4.1 (10 pts)
Must be in github repo link
Create a VPC in your preferred region (must have at least 3 availability zones). Inside your VPC, build a single Windows bastion host within a public subnet, and one Linux web server per availability zone, all  in different private subnets. Each Linux web server should also display different text and pictures. Take screenshots of the running WIndows bastion host, the three Linux servers (highlighting the three different AZs in each photo), and a screenshot of a successful SSH connection to each Linux server from within the bastion host.
